<h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
<p>Hello <%= @user.name || "there" %>,</p>
<p>
We received a request to reset the password for your Untethered account linked to <%= @user.email %>.
</p>
<p>
To reset your password, please click the link below:<br>
<%= link_to edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email, subdomain: @operator.subdomain), edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email, subdomain: @operator.subdomain) %>
</p>
<p>
If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. This link will expire in two hours for your security.
</p>
<p>
Thank you<br>
